Discover files in a directory with relevance scoring, pattern matching,
and dependency analysis. Pure Go implementation — no external binary needed.

Example:
  sin-code discover . --pattern "**/*.go" --sort_by relevance --format json

Usage:
  sin-code discover [path] [flags]

Flags:
  -f, --format string    Output format: text|json (default "text")
  -h, --help             help for discover
  -l, --limit int        Max results (default 100)
  -p, --pattern string   File pattern (glob) (default "**/*")
  -s, --sort_by string   Sort by: relevance|name|size|mtime (default "relevance")
  -v, --version          version for discover
